Web CPAR - Password Reset Request
===============================================
Hello, <%= @user.name %>, did you ask to reset your password?

To reset your password click the URL below.

<%= edit_password_reset_url(@user.password_reset_token) %>

You may change your password with the link above within the next 3 hours. Please request a new Password Reset email if your link has expired.

If you did not request your password to be reset please ignore this email and your password will stay as it is.